data.description: Experience the ultimate seclusion in this private sanctuary, nestled in this tranquil Stillwater location. This inviting house sits on a large lot, creating a serene haven where you can unwind and reconnect with nature. Spacious and welcoming, this 1849 sqft home features three bedrooms, providing ample room for family and guests. The property's thoughtful layout and design ensure comfort and functionality, making it a perfect choice for those seeking a well-designed and comfortable living space. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this cozy home features a spacious living area that's perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing in peace. The open plan kitchen, dining, and living areas create a warm and inviting atmosphere that's ideal for spending quality time with family and friends. The well-appointed kitchen ensures efficiency and organization, while the stylish pendant lights create an enchanting atmosphere for culinary adventures and cherished moments with loved ones. This delightful property features a pool and large lawn, ideal for enjoying the great outdoors. The fenced yard provides added privacy, while the patio and shed offer additional space for outdoor activities and storage. Don't miss the opportunity to own this charming home! Qualified buyers should inquire about assumable loan, speak with your lender today.
